    {
      "point": "要是...就... construction",
      "explanation": "Expresses condition and result: if...then.",
      "example": "要是方便的话,明天你去办公室时,帮我把这张表送到办公室。",
      "translation": "If convenient, tomorrow when you go to the office, help me deliver this form to the office."
    },
    {
      "point": "Pivotal sentences with 请/叫/让",
      "explanation": "These causative verbs link two verb phrases where the object of the first becomes the subject of the second.",
